{
  "stem": "210.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we ran to the next town, which was-- I don't know how many kilometers-- maybe 14, 15 kilometers-- and-- till this [? kind of ?] bombing calm-- quieted down.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we kept running there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we ran a whole day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then we came to some kind of a village when it was dark.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the-- the owners of the farm put us up in a barn.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I'll never forget the flies there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was just horrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And let's say, the next day, we wanted to go back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But we couldn't go back, because the German soldiers were coming with all their tanks, and all their equipment, and marching.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We couldn't go back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It took about a week till we finally were able to go back to our city.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "All this time we didn't hear about my father, and we thought for sure maybe he got killed or something happened to him.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "On the way home-- this was about a week later-- so we-- on the way home, we saw a-- a woman that knew my mother.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "She was a gentile woman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And she told my mother that my father is alive, that she saw him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we came home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we came in front of our house, and it was burned.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everything was burned to the ground-- the-- like half that street was burned to the ground.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we went to my grandfather's house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father was there, and we stayed with my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At that time was the first time I saw my father after that week.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was, at that time, the-- the-- a law was-- came out that everybody had to shave off the beards, and you know.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
